UPGRADE_TRANSACTION_RUNNER=""
UPGRADE_TRANSACTION_ACTIVE=0
UPGRADE_TRANSACTION_WAS_RUNNING=0
UPGRADE_CANDIDATE_CONFIG=""
UPGRADE_CANDIDATE_RUNTIME=""
INSTALL_WAIT_TAGLINES=(
  "Go scroll some reels while I take care of this for you."
  "Failed.......................... JK, it's going well ;)"
  "Extracting pure epicness..."
  "Just a few hours more............................LOL JK! It will be just a few minutes. :)"
  "What's your favorite political party? I'm pro AI."
  "Man... we hope this open source project makes some money. Not sure how though :D"
  "Can't wait help build you a niche vertical SaaS AI company!"
  "I can feel your computer getting hotter. wink wink."
  "This is the exact moment people start checking the installer every 12 seconds."
  "If it looks frozen, that is just npm exploring its emotions."
  "Packaging enough dependencies to make your fans question their life choices."
  "Your coffee break has entered its most productive phase."
  "Compiling the part that somehow worked on my machine five minutes ago."
  "Docker is waking up like it just had the deepest nap of its life."
  "This is a healthy amount of suspense for an installer."
  "I wonder if by 2029 there will be no more waiting for installations to finish."
